Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經要Game over了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這邊走
