Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了打開嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是非常事態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
